sources.title: Never Too Late (1935) RICHARD TALMADGE
sources.description:
PizzaFLIX Presents Classic Movie Monday
Starring: Richard Talmadge, Thelma White, Robert Frazer 
Director: Franklin Shamray

A daredevil detective gets mixed up with a pearl necklace, a gang of jewel thieves, and a girl with "something on her mind, and it isn't a prayer book."

TRIVIA: Richard Talmadge, born Sylvester Ricardo Metzetti, was a member of the Flying Metzettis, a family of acrobats renowned for originating the quadruple back somersault!
